CS2003 OPERATING SYSTEMS 
PROJECT

IMPORTANT INSTRUCTIONS TO IMPLEMENT THE ICE CREAM FACTORY PROJECT

1. USE ORACLE VIRTUAL BOX (RECOMMENDED)
2. USE UBUNTU VERSION 16.04 LTS
3. DOWNLOAD A KERNEL WITH A LATEST VERSION THAN THAT OF YOURS
4. IMPLEMENT SYSTEM CALL USING THE CONFIGURATIONS GIVEN IN PROJECT REPORT
5. THE SYSTEM CALL METHOD IS NOT SAME AS THAT OF HELLO WORLD.
6. GIVE MORE CPU'S TO VIRTUAL MACHINE TO SPEED UP THE PROCESS OF COMPILATION OF KERNEL
7. MAKE SURE TO BE IN ROOT MODE WHILE IMPLEMENTING COMMANDS SUCH AS make clean -j4, make -j4 (root mode : sudo su)

